    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Put 1 <span class=\"text-danger\">[2]</span> large baking tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> in the oven to heat up (this will stop the pizza bottoms from going soggy!)</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
