    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>tomato paste</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper </strong>and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Add 5 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [10 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>tomato sauce</strong></p>",
